outputs.output_descr:
Following the launching of the  E-Government Strategy in October, 2009  the ultimate goal of the project is to  initiate the implementation phase of the strategy through enhancing  the  operational capacity and the institutional framework for overall coordination of e-government initiatives. 
Syrian e-government strategy has three strategic priorities:
•	Electronic Services Delivery 
•	Public Administration Reform 
•	Development  of Enabling Environment
